Package: sportVU
Title: Shot Charts and Movement Plots using SportVU Data
Version: 1.0
Author: Nicholas Canova <ncanova@stanford.edu>,
		Fjori Shemaj <fshemaj@stanford.edu>,
		Peter Lee <pejhlee@stanford.edu>
Maintainer: Nicholas Canova <ncanova@stanford.edu>
Description: Analyzes and visualizes NBA sportVU data. 
             Includes multiple parsing functions to convert sportVU XML data into R dataframes. 
             Further, includes player shot charts for both individual games and full seasons, as well as 
             movement plots of players for individual games.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2)
Imports:
	XML,
	dplyr,
	ggplot2,
	plyr,
	shiny,
	shinythemes,
	data.table,
	utils,
	stats
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
